{"tid":1984105,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消防員涉管有汽油彈案 加控無牌管有無線電器具罪 暫毋須答辯 5月4日再訊","createTime":"2020-04-22T08:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T01:25:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f449836b54a93c37be36c99b43dd65260bc4eed","tid":1984105,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"消防員涉管有汽油彈案 被告加控無牌管有無線電器具罪<br />\n22.04.2020 16:46<br />\n<br />\n一名33歲消防員去年11月在旺角涉嫌管有包括汽油彈等武器及拒捕，案件在九龍城法院提訊，被告除原有的4項控罪，今日被加控一項無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪，被告暫毋須答辯，案件押後至下月4日再聆訊，到時再決定會否將另外3宗，同樣在今日再提堂的同類案件合併處理，被告須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告方志雄案發當日在彌敦道及山東街一帶，管有4支汽油彈、一個鐵錘及一支鐵筆，並攜帶了一把刀，被告亦涉及非法集結，並抗拒警員執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282634&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282634%26csid%3D261_341&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cl7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=d039ed7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282634&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"be784e6fb7f2638950075272e565bc9954d01b0a","tid":1984105,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"咁都唔俾保釋"},{"pid":"714bda0a262e52a23f131599c3a894702a710331","tid":1984105,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04721c2ac798b114f6f25f4d9f6f0d757784208","tid":1984105,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"真手足 咪撚再話火燒狗屋係自導自演"},{"pid":"b77d08b05d8ac00d92aab5502d8b64c9aa2d32f7","tid":1984105,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04721c2ac798b114f6f25f4d9f6f0d757784208","tid":1984105,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"真手足 咪撚再話火燒狗屋